    <item>
      <title>奥利弗·怀曼（Oliver Wyman）将950亿美元的利润视为商品贸易的“基准”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/oliver-wyman-sees-95-billion-profit-year-as-baseline-for-commodities-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Oliver Wyman LLC称，去年的商品交易利润为950亿美元为“未来增长的基准”提供了“基线”，即使在一段极端波动之后市场正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/oliver-wyman-sees-95-billion-profit-year-as-baseline-for-commodities-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当哈萨克斯坦进一步违反配额时，欧佩克+石油生产激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/opec-oil-production-surges-as-kazakhstan-further-breaches-quota</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，欧佩克+原油生产激增，哈萨克斯坦长期以来一直违反了卡特尔的产出配额，进一步违反了其商定的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/opec-oil-production-surges-as-kazakhstan-further-breaches-quota</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非提议较小的增值税以结束预算僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/south-africa-proposes-smaller-vat-hike-to-end-budget-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长伊诺克·戈尼格瓦纳（Enoch Godongwana）提议扩大消费税的缩减和遏制支出，以赢得在先前的迭代被击落后，从美国脆弱的管理联盟中赢得对预算的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/south-africa-proposes-smaller-vat-hike-to-end-budget-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 12:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的收益率接近3％的历史枢轴里的里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/german-yield-nears-3-milestone-on-historic-pivot-to-more-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的基准债券收益率在近18个月以来首次达到3％的触点距离，这是对借贷历史激增的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/german-yield-nears-3-milestone-on-historic-pivot-to-more-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 11:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向德黑兰发出信件时，中国主持伊朗核谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-to-host-russia-and-iran-for-talks-on-moribund-nuclear-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普敦促德黑兰就其原子能工作或面临军事行动进行新协议时，将与伊朗和俄罗斯进行核谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-to-host-russia-and-iran-for-talks-on-moribund-nuclear-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 08:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国电力拍卖会付出近记录的胜利费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/uk-power-auction-pays-out-near-record-fee-in-win-for-gas-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将继续在本十年下半年补贴化石燃料的发电厂，运营商支付了近乎记录的费用以保持开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/uk-power-auction-pays-out-near-record-fee-in-win-for-gas-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 08:38:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
